      + control Auto-Mute Mode            | id:  4              | type: enum | selected: 0
      + control Input Source              | id:  5              | type: enum | selected: 0
      + control Input Source              | id:  6              | type: enum | selected: 0
      + control Capture Volume            | id:  7 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Capture Volume            | id:  7 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Capture Volume            | id:  9 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Capture Volume            | id:  9 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Master Playback Volume    | id: 13 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 60 | min: 0 | max: 87
      + control Master Playback Switch    | id: 14 | channel: 0 | type: bool | value: true
      + control Dmic0 Capture Volume      | id: 24 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 70 | min: 0 | max: 70
      + control Dmic0 Capture Volume      | id: 24 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 70 | min: 0 | max: 70
      + control Dmic1 2nd Capture Volume  | id: 27 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 70 | min: 0 | max: 70
      + control Dmic1 2nd Capture Volume  | id: 27 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 70 | min: 0 | max: 70
    + profile u7413 | . SOF Raptor Lake (same as Alder Lake)
      + routing | playback: pcmC0D0p | mic_internal: pcmC0D6c | mic_headset: pcmC0D0c
                | speaker_external_id: 1 | speaker_internal_id:  3
                | mic_external_id:     8 | mic_internal_id:     25
      + control Headphone Playback Volume | id:  0 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 40 | min: 0 | max: 87
      + control Headphone Playback Volume | id:  0 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 40 | min: 0 | max: 87
      + control Speaker Playback Volume   | id:  2 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 87 | min: 0 | max: 87
      + control Speaker Playback Volume   | id:  2 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 87 | min: 0 | max: 87
      + control Auto-Mute Mode            | id:  4              | type: enum | selected: 0
      + control Input Source              | id:  5              | type: enum | selected: 0
