      + control Capture Volume            | id:  9 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Capture Volume            | id:  9 | channel: 1 | type: int  | value: 63 | min: 0 | max: 63
      + control Master Playback Volume    | id: 13 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 60 | min: 0 | max: 87
