    + profile ds57u | . HDA
      + routing | playback: pcmC0D0p | mic_internal: pcmC0D0c | mic_headset: pcmC0D0c
                | speaker_external_id: 1 | mic_external_id: 6
      + control Master Playback Volume    | id:  0 | channel: 0 | type: int  | value: 60 | min: 0 | max: 87
